":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:16:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">係地鐵放tear gas 係好大張牌<br />\n文宣 貼多啲post係連儂牆 </span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:29:21.000Z","msg":"聯署真係搞得裡，特別係第1點，應該幫到好然義士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:41:49.000Z","msg":"唔係p嘅巴打請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c84d53cced70a8c3b569ab68d2e12f9c15f094c","tid":1461052,"uid":175996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:56:07.000Z","msg":"pushh"},{"pid":"55ec1676402819f7dac8296265cadd804aa86086","tid":1461052,"uid":24597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:09:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ac2323f89b28baee96c1ebea2dcc8853d87c08c","tid":1461052,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"667fb90a8eb97c101e85d4a35a3c8db8b3f4344c","tid":1461052,"uid":301432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:59:22.000Z","msg":"事源: 係8月12日早上8點，本人將draft左既兩份聯署email左俾所有泛民議員，並懇請佢地818舉行遊行同時舉辦聯署。<br />\n<br />\n詳情見下post:<br />\n【行動POST】 【必入必推】 (8.18暫定)反警及重申五大訴求聯署及遊行行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1452156/page/1?post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1452156/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<strong><ins>簡單黎講就係，懇請泛民議員代搞:</ins></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>818遊行: 針對黑警濫暴</strong></span></span> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聯署1: (義士唔係CONDOM)<br />\n反映香港市民不相信香港警方為誠實可靠以及公眾對香港警方的不信任，<br />\n懇請法院審理案件時，審慎地考慮每位警員的可信性，<br />\n保持獨立、中立及不偏頗</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>聯署2: 重申五大訴求，若政府拒絕回應，<br />\n只好拼死一搏，寧為玉碎，不為瓦存</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n在此為民陣舉辦818遊行感到高興，<br />\n但對於完全無提及聯署感中心灰。<br />\n<br />\n不過有見及新POST連登回應度都唔高，<br />\n所以對民陣對於我聯署提議無回應表示絕對理解同體諒。<br />\n<br />\n在此衷心感謝民陣及全體泛民議員聆聽民意，為民發聲。<br />\n並強烈呼籲連登全體仝人盡全力支持民陣818活動。<br />\n請吹盡雞，廣傳818遊行消息俾你所有親戚朋友。<br />\n<br />\n另外在此特別嗚謝2百多位入左TG既朋友，但有見及上述情況，<br />\n聯署事宜可能待稍後被捕人士臨近上庭，先會睇下搞唔搞到落去。<br />\n有任何意見想俾既朋友可以TG聯絡我提出。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:37:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"080972c0886d255b732431a1257cd88869e4dc73","tid":1461052,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"931c30cc4ab7ea5451bcd2cd913ebb2581412851","tid":1461052,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:16:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">係地鐵放tear gas 係好大張牌<br />\n文宣 貼多啲post係連儂牆 </span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:38:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6ca009b03d8a5dfc48811f8b7779b1327121cd3","tid":1461052,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"080972c0886d255b732431a1257cd88869e4dc73","tid":1461052,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"931c30cc4ab7ea5451bcd2cd913ebb2581412851","tid":1461052,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:16:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">係地鐵放tear gas 係好大張牌<br />\n文宣 貼多啲post係連儂牆 </span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:38:22.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5882122d0593866ec4e1c57aaacd966d6991901","tid":1461052,"uid":287057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:55:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"695cf9c38faff7d98c13d11b1fcd2ef2f344f1e1","tid":1461052,"uid":3035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:13:05.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"5769abd91fdccae5bea19d09cd76290a860da440","tid":1461052,"uid":236471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:18:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class